  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study investigates carriage rate and risk factors for acquiring multiresistant bacteria
      (ESBL producing E.coli and K.pneumoniae, carbapenem-resistant and multidrug resistant
      P.aeruginosa, MRSA and VRE) in hospitalised patients and healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
